                     <interp inst="t18670610-573-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>, Stealing materials for making two police<lb></lb>coats, the property of <persName id="t18670610-name-264" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18670610-name-264" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
